snippet.title: Coldplay
snippet.description:
The official Coldplay channel. The new album, Moon Music, out now. 

With over 100 million records sold, 9 Brit Awards and 7 Grammys, Coldplay are an iconic, alternative rock band with hit songs including Viva La Vida, Hymn For The Weekend, Paradise, The Scientist, Fix You, Adventure Of A Lifetime, My Universe and Yellow. The band's legendary catalogue also includes nine #1 albums: Parachutes, A Rush of Blood to the Head, X&Y, Viva la Vida, Mylo Xyloto, Ghost Stories, A Head Full of Dreams, Everyday Life and Music Of The Spheres. 

Subscribe to Coldplay’s channel for the latest official videos.
